Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Maigret command not found

Solution: Ensure pip3 installation completed successfully
Add ~/.local/bin to PATH: export PATH=$PATH:~/.local/bin
Issue: Timeout errors during searches

Solution: Increase timeout value: --timeout 60
Reduce concurrent requests or add delays between searches
Issue: JSON parsing errors in scripts

Solution: Verify JSON file exists and is valid
Add error handling with try-except blocks
Check file permissions: chmod 644 *.json
Issue: Empty or incomplete results

Solution: Some platforms may block automated requests
Use --verbose flag to see detailed errors
Verify internet connectivity and DNS resolution
